        "job_name": "Pursuit and suppression",
        "job_description": "You heard that the Knights of the Red Stripe were placing a bounty on a traitor with great fanfare - he was once a high-ranking officer affiliated with the Order's Naval Engineering Academy - but it all came to nothing after he stole one of the Order's experimental capital ships and defected. There are rumors that he was once a pirate who surrendered due to the intimidation of the Knights. Before that, he had no luck in plundering, but after being captured, he was extremely flattering and even betrayed many of his brothers. In this way, it seems that he has returned to his old profession, provided that he can really survive.", # 默认：空白。选择任务后显示的详细描述。                                                       
